author: Reuters Editorial
title: British ambassador's car arrives at Russian foreign ministry: witness
text:
MOSCOW (Reuters) - The official car of the British ambassador to Moscow arrived at the Russian foreign ministry building on Friday, a Reuters camera operator at the scene said.
British Ambassador to Russia Laurie Bristow leaves the Russian foreign ministry building in Moscow, Russia March 30, 2018. REUTERS/Maxim Shemetov The Reuters camera operator said he saw the British ambassador, Laurie Bristow, in the car. The reason for the visit was not immediately clear and there was not immediate announcement from the British embassy.
Reporting by Dmitry Madorsky; Writing by Christian Lowe
